te your handlers. For a list of all classes, see [Class Library Overview](../mfc/class-library-overview.md) in the *MFC Reference*.  \n  \n## See Also  \n [Messages and Commands in the Framework](../mfc/messages-and-commands-in-the-framework.md)\n\n"}